text: Tainui is a small suburb of Dunedin. It lies south of Andersons Bay and Musselburgh close to Dunedin's coastline (Ocean Beach}. In 1905 the ground hosted its one and only rugby test and hosts Dunedin's A&P; show yearly. It has two primary schools located in the suburb. ==References== Category:Suburbs of Dunedin
title: Tainui, New Zealand
